narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Absolutely take this class if you're interested in reading great works of fiction that you will probably never be exposed to again. I came into this class having heard of only one of the authors, but I would now count several of the novels we have read and discussed as among the best I have ever read.
It's a great way to read awesome books. Not too much work involved. Lectures can get a little bit long and tedious. But, books are really good.
